Cherry Bullet（韓語：체리블렛；日語：チェリー・ブレット），為韓國FNC娛樂旗下的十人女子組合。成員從2018年11月21日開始依次公開 。由六名韓國成員海允、裕姝、未來、紫蘿、智媛、彩麟，三名日本成員KOKORO、莉美、MAY，以及一名台灣成員粼粼所組成，並由未來擔任隊長。2019年1月21日以首張迷你專輯《Let's Play Cherry Bullet》正式出道。
「Cherry Bullet」是將Cherry（櫻桃）和Bullet（子彈）形成鮮明對比的詞，以櫻桃般可愛而又富有個性的魅力，狙擊大眾心的女子組合。

I saw Cherry Bullet live twice at Yokohama Stadium with my friends which was absolutely incredible and unforgettable. It was a worthwhile concert which was compelling enough to see again. I remember the first time went to see their concert we were late. I said "Look at the time. The concert will have begun" It was quarter of nine. The concert would've started by then. The members in Cherry Bullet have been strutting their stuff since they were children so don't sell them short. At the end of the last encore they bowed onstage soaking up the applause. They were given a standing ovation and thunderous applause. The group and the dancers and acrobats who were invited to perform alongside the group on the stage gave a superb performance. The choreography, the stage and lighting design and the light sticks were magnificent and exceeded our expectations. My cousin who's very career-oriented is planning on having them endorse her company's products but she'll have to make it financially worthwhile for them. Cherry Bullet has a worthwhile job and career. I consider music performing a worthwhile career. On top of being a great musician, May is an avid runner. She took part in a three thousand metre race where she came first. She rose to the challenge of passing the runners who were ahead of her earlier, ran for all she was worth and dived across the finish line. Loads of fans and her friends congratulated her on having won the race as she held the trophy up. The race is the opportunity for all the world's best female runner to strut their stuff. It was truly memorable. May told me regarding a piece of music by Ravel "this passage should be played beautifully rather than rhythmically. Otherwise it's a bit cheap." I saw lots of her pencil marks on the score such as: cantabile, silence, no pause here, clean pedal, just separate, more melodic voicing, remain soft, stay soft, quiet, hear tenor, clearer, articulate, in time, silvery soft, gentler, take time....Regarding teaching she said "I prefer payment in blocks. My students pay monthly or for four lessons at a time. For this month it's ok to pay on a lesson-by-lesson basis because maybe you wanna see what it's like to have lessons. From next month onwards pay monthly. I'm also an accompanist who accompanies instrumentalists and singers for auditions and live performances. Some of my adult students started playing cornet when they were eighteen. Their fingers are less dextrous and slower than say a ten year old kid. Start training your fingers when you're still very young so that you can get much faster fingers. It'll improve your finger dexterity, speed, strength and accuracy to a great extent." She asked me to get her some scores as I can get them on the cheap from a friend of mine. Cherry Bullet's concert tour of Asia has been greeted with widespread critical acclaim in the press including Oriental daily, Southern daily, South China morning post, Hong Kong Economic Journal and various cultural websites. Their song "Run" has won great international acclaim by the media including Japan Today, Japan Times Online, The Japan News and various cultural websites. By the way I'm held up in a traffic jam. The traffic normally is fairly light but today it's been unusually heavy. The car behind me is blowing his horn along the way. Next time I'll go early so as to avoid the traffic.
